<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:849px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">terminate your account, you must terminate your account as set forth in Section </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:826px;letter-spacing:-0.1px;">16. </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:792px;letter-spacing:-0.1px;">Homee App Co operates a nation business, and our pricing varies by a number of </span>
<span class="t s3" data-mappings='[[24,"ff"]]' style="left:110px;bottom:769px;letter-spacing:-0.13px;word-spacing:0.03px;">factors. We frequently oﬀer promotional rates - which can vary based on region, </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:747px;letter-spacing:-0.13px;word-spacing:0.03px;">length of subscription, bundle size and more. We also regularly test new features </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:724px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">and payment options. Homee App Co reserves the right, including without prior </span>
