<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:777px;letter-spacing:-0.09px;">c. A boosted listing is available for a total of eight listings per suburb. If all eight </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:755px;letter-spacing:-0.1px;">boosted listings have been exhausted for a particular suburb, you will not be able </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:732px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">to purchase a Boost Listing until there is a position available. </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:698px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.02px;">d. All payments for access to Boost Services are processed by Stripe or Braintree </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:675px;letter-spacing:-0.15px;word-spacing:0.05px;">(a PayPal company). Homee does not store credit card details. </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:641px;letter-spacing:-0.1px;">e. Once a payment for access to Boost Services is complete, your boosted listing </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:618px;letter-spacing:-0.12px;word-spacing:0.03px;">will be ranked in one of the top eight spots for its suburb room search results for </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:596px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">seven days from and including the date of registration. The ranking within </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:573px;letter-spacing:-0.1px;word-spacing:0.01px;">boosted listings for a suburb is based upon the most recently boosted listing for </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:551px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">that suburb. Homee will not refund a Boost Listings payment under any </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:528px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">circumstances including, without limitation, if Homee terminates your Access to </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:506px;letter-spacing:-0.16px;word-spacing:0.06px;">the App or the Services for breaching these Terms and Conditions of Use. </span>
<span class="t s3" data-mappings='[[45,"fi"]]' style="left:110px;bottom:471px;letter-spacing:-0.12px;word-spacing:0.02px;">f. If your listing is undergoing a Homee veriﬁcation check the listing may </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:449px;letter-spacing:-0.09px;">temporarily be unavailable on our site. If this is the case, your Boost Service will </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:426px;letter-spacing:-0.1px;">be paused for the time it was not available, and the expiry date of your Boost </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:404px;letter-spacing:-0.15px;word-spacing:0.06px;">Service will be extended to cover this period of delay. </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:369px;letter-spacing:-0.17px;word-spacing:0.06px;">a. EXTERNAL SERVICE PURCHASES AND SUBSCRIPTIONS </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:334px;letter-spacing:-0.12px;word-spacing:0.02px;">External Service Purchases, including subscriptions, may be processed through </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:312px;letter-spacing:-0.12px;word-spacing:0.02px;">the External Service, in which case those purchases must be managed through </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:290px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">your External Service Account. Subscriptions automatically renew until you </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:267px;letter-spacing:-0.1px;">cancel. </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:232px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">When making a purchase on the Service, you may have the option to pay </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:210px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.01px;">through an External Service, such as with your Apple ID or Google Play account </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:187px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.02px;">("your External Service Account"), and your External Service Account will be </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:165px;letter-spacing:-0.12px;word-spacing:0.02px;">charged for the purchase in accordance with the terms disclosed to you at the </span>
<span class="t s3" style="left:110px;bottom:143px;letter-spacing:-0.11px;word-spacing:0.02px;">time of purchase and the general terms applicable to your External Service </span></div>

